# Azure Databricks ETL Pipeline Project

## Project Overview
Built an end-to-end ETL pipeline using Microsoft Azure, Azure Databricks, PySpark, SQL, and Delta Lake to process sales data and generate business KPIs.

---

## Technologies Used
- Microsoft Azure
- Azure Databricks
- PySpark
- SQL
- Delta Lake
- Data Engineering
- ETL Pipeline

---

## Project Architecture

Raw Data → Bronze Layer → Silver Layer → Gold Layer → Analytics Dashboard

---

## Features
- Data Ingestion
- Data Cleaning
- ETL Processing
- PySpark Transformations
- SQL Analytics
- Delta Tables
- KPI Analysis

---

## KPIs Generated
- Total Sales
- Top Products
- Monthly Revenue
- Regional Performance
- Customer Insights

---

## Learning Outcomes
- Built scalable ETL workflows
- Learned cloud-based data engineering
- Worked with Azure Databricks
- Implemented Medallion Architecture
- Performed business analytics using Spark SQL

---

## Project Files
- `.dbc` Databricks Notebook
- `.html` Notebook Export
- SQL Queries
- PySpark Transformations

---

## Future Improvements
- Power BI Dashboard Integration
- Real-time Streaming Pipeline
- Azure Data Factory Integration
